y_Fleetwood\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tommy Fleetwood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\"}, {\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This live blog has now closed.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All hail the new king in town.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a bow, Noah Lyles.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American talked the talk and he walked the walk in the men's 100m final.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999997747663909, \"rank\": 2.2451085642511488e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can read James Gray's report from Stade de France here.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Gray_Bethune\", \"score\": 0.9999999781393856, \"rank\": 1.851544082243027e-08, \"text\": \"James Gray\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Gray_Bethune\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Gray_Bethune\"}, {\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will be back tomorrow to see if Team GB can add more medals to their haul.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.963415818533111e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles was the slowest of anyone out of the blocks and still last after 30 metres, but finished fastest to pip Kishane Thompson in a seven-way photo finish.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 972, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9999956736931288, \"rank\": 4.326325867407299e-06, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the one I wanted.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the hard battle.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the amazing opponents.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everybody's healthy, everybody came prepared for the fight and I want to prove that I am the man amongst all of them.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the wolf among wolves,\\\" said Lyles, whose USA team-mate Fred Kerley took bronze.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.999961237319489, \"rank\": 3.8764183190434085e-05, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.474035094038322, \"rank\": 0.7119644634354305, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went up to Kishane and I was like 'Imma be honest bro, I think you had that one' and I was fully expecting to see his name pop up.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To see my name pop, I was like 'Goodness gracious, I am incredible'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles is also the reigning world champion in the 200m, and will start as a considerable favourite to do the double.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's my better event,\\\" Lyes added.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And now that I have got a new PR [personal record] in the 100m, I am ready to take it to the 200m.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles gives his thumbs up to VAR, Olympic 100m champion by a nipple.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.76204245650245e-26, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven-way photo finish\\u2026 and Noah Lyles has won it!\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USA's Lyles has beaten Kishane Thompson by five thousandths of a second in a time of 9.784, with Fred Kerley taking bronze for the Americans.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.474035094038322, \"rank\": 0.7119644634354305, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"htt