and event of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are three Americans in the final, with world champion Noah Lyles the fastest of the three this year, although 29-year-old Fred Kerley has been as fast as 9.76.\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The favourite though is Kishane Thompson, 23, aiming to bring gold back to Jamaica for the first time since Usain Bolt in Rio 2016, and his team-mate Oblique Seville, also 23 years old, could well grab a medal too.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9999956736931288, \"rank\": 4.326325867407299e-06, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 2783, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9543409086646387e-21, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 